# Final UI Adjustments and APK Build Plan

## Goal Description
1.  **Bible Page Dropdown**: Ensure clicking the Book name opens the book list, and clicking the Chapter name opens the chapter list. (This logic seems already in place, but I will double-check [toggleBookMenu](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/pages/BiblePage.jsx#67-68) and [toggleChapterMenu](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/pages/BiblePage.jsx#68-69) functions).
